000796</a>  </li><li> Orsi NSA 1889 384 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001392</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">12</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 685 add <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Rizzo 1923 126 no.2 fig.58 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001638\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001638</a>  </li><li> Manganaro 1963 57-58 ph <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001850\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001850</a>  </li><li> Le Guen 2001 319 no.73 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001883\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001883</a>  </li><li> Aneziri 2003 401 F2 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000641\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000641</a>  </li><li> Orsi 2018 Tacc. 1, p. 40 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002617\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002617</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Neat and regular letters of the later Hellenistic period, in some cases with pronounced serifs. Omicron is full-size; omega is closed; epsilon has shorter middle bar; mu has splayed outer hastae; kappa on occasion has short arms; sigma has parallel top and bottom strokes; pi has equal vertical strokes and the horizontal overhangs on both sides.</p> <p> Types list: <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-Α-type1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Α type1</a> <a href=\"https://kingsdigitallab.github.io/crossreads/data/allographs/types/greek-